3
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:30,840
Welcome to Last Week Tonight.

4
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:33,440
I'm John Oliver.
Thank you for joining us.

5
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:37,480
We dive straight in this week
with Stupid Watergate II,

6
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:41,280
the scandal that's like getting
a rubber chicken stuck in your ass,

7
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:44,040
it's kind of funny,
but also actually serious

8
00:00:44,120 --> 00:00:46,280
and something
needs to be done about it.

9
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:51,560
The House continued calling witnesses
ahead of public impeachment hearings.

10
00:00:51,680 --> 00:00:54,880
But the president has figured out
who is really to blame

11
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:58,720
and chose his helicopter-yell time
to share it with everyone.

12
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:02,800
It's called the swamp.
And you know what I did ?

13
