he'd relied upon an intermediary,

66
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:58,800
this man, Randy Credico,
a radio host and comedian.

67
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:01,400
Credico has denied
being that intermediary

68
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:03,640
