well to that.

69
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:09,120
Prosecutors read Stone's messages
to Credico in court and they are rough.

70
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:12,880
Stone writes to Credico:
"You are a rat, a stoolie."

71
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:17,560
